NAME:
   enaptercli.test rule-engine rule create - Create a new rule

USAGE:
   enaptercli.test rule-engine rule create [command options]

OPTIONS:
   --slug value             Slug of a new rule
   --name value             Name of a new rule
   --code value             Path to a file containing the script code
   --runtime-version value  Version of a runtime to use for the script execution (default: 3)
   --exec-interval value    How often to execute the script. This option is only compatible with the runtime version 1 (default: 0s)
   --disable                Whether to disable a rule upon creation (default: false)
   --help, -h               show help

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES:
   ENAPTER3_API_TOKEN  Enapter API access token
   ENAPTER3_API_HOST   Enapter API base URL (https://api.enapter.com by default)

